metadata.test_query:
with a as (
    select * from "quantium"."pil"."pil"
),
b as (
    select * from "quantium"."pil"."pil_two"
),
final as (
    select
        COALESCE(a.TxnStartDate, b.TxnStartDate) AS TxnStartDate,
        COUNT(a.*) - COUNT(b.*) AS RecordCountDiff,
        -1 AS LowerThreshold,
        1 AS UpperThreshold,
        CASE 
          WHEN (COUNT(a.*) - COUNT(b.*)) <= -1 THEN 'Fail'
          WHEN (COUNT(a.*) - COUNT(b.*)) >= 1 THEN 'Fail'
          ELSE 'Pass'
        END AS Outcome
    FROM
        a
    FULL JOIN
        b ON a.TxnStartDate = b.TxnStartDate
    GROUP BY 1
)

select *
from final
